title: For Sale:  AK-47,(7.62x39) 30 rnd, bakelite magazines, Tula  100% Russian
postcontent: Russian AK-47(7.62x39mm) $50.00     each I can send you     pictures and you decide which one you want.  This is a great option if you are buying only one mag and you want something special.  Whether it's for your collection, a gift, or your go to magazine.  They are easily identified among other magazines so they are great for your specialty ammo such as barrier defeating, tracer ammo, large exposed soft points, blanks and everything else in between.  They feed ammunition with out restriction, all have metal reinforced feed lips.  If your choice of ammunition does't/won't work with these magazines, well then, for the most part won't work in other magazines made to military specifications.  You may want to try a commercial copy that works with your choice of ammo and stick with those.  But you are better off investing your money in ammunition that performs well in genuine mil-spec magazines.  These magazines cannot be faked and they will not be made again.  Perhaps you want a paticlar shade, or mold number or a certain inspector stamp, again you decide.  Occasionaly I have some original Russian spare magazine parts and bodies, they may need some cleaning up.
